  "texts": [
    "Candidates predictable by one of the activity models were considered \"mediumconfident\".",
    "In total, 2491 predictions fall into the three categories assigned based on their best supporting evidence (Fig. 3a).",
    "Below we enumerate a few \"known\" cases that otherwise would have been placed into different categories, as they provide an initial validation of successful target deconvolution for orphan compounds solely based on transcriptional signatures.",
    "17 (0.7%) predictions are \"structure sure\".",
    "Examples include afimoxifene (BRD-K93754473), which was correctly predicted to target estrogen receptor 1 (ESR1) (score 0.91) and confirmed by its structural similarity with tamoxifen (BRD-K04210847) (SAR probability 0.97)."
